title: Microsoft Windows XP x64 Professional, No Activation
description:
This is a clean, full install of Windows XP x64 Professional Corporate edition.  The CD key is included in the .uif, simply download and burn with MagicISO.  Passes WGA, there is no activation necessary.

NOTE:  This is the 64-bit version, which does have software incompatibilities. If you load this OS, and something doesn&#039;t work, then blame Microsoft.
